{
  "title": "Maxema - Mood Metal - Personalized and promotional pens. Promotional writing instruments and custom printed pens.",
  "description": "Mood Metal A precious, refined pen, even though it is designed for promotion. Mood Metal is the Maxema collection’s ultimate expression of exclusivity and refinement. The shine of the metal - with its diamond mirror finish - that characterises the tip, barrel and cap is striking, while the plastic clip offers space and colour for customisation. The Parker refill completes the equipment of a pen conceived on the basis of high quality standards and carefully crafted with artisan techniques. The metal finish comes in three versions: chrome, gold and titanium grey.",
