  "mainText": "Italiano English Reserved Area Contacts Company Pens Customisation Sample kits Finishes Recycled pens More maxema ® via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com P PRODUCTS Our pens Kind / Kind / Icon Pure / Flow Pure / Dot / Zink / Pixel / Bay / Mood Metal / Kind / Mood / Flow / View / Tag Green / Next / Tag / Icon / Icon green / Ethic Search by color rose/purple azure / blue green yellow/orange red cream/brown grey black white select a color S Services customisation packaging pantone colors sample kits C COMPANY Maxema Company contacts FAVORITES SAMPLE KITS ACCOUNT FAQ MEDIA DISCLAIMER previous model/ next model HomePens Catalogue Mood Metal MoodMetal luxury is a state of mind Technical information Download pdfof this model A precious, refined pen, even though it is designed for promotion. Mood Metal is the Maxema collection’s ultimate expression of exclusivity and refinement. The shine of the metal - with its diamond mirror finish - that characterises the tip, barrel and cap is striking, while the plastic clip offers space and colour for customisation. The Parker refill completes the equipment of a pen conceived on the basis of high quality standards and carefully crafted with artisan techniques. The metal finish comes in three versions: chrome, gold and titanium grey. 1/4 Details 2/4 Variants 3/4 Technical information 4/4 Customisations log in P/Mood Metal 1/4 Details Details of the pen Tip, barrel and cap in metal with a diamond mirror finish 23 clip colours to give your pen even more character Single My Box case in black Fedrigoni cardboard 2/4 Models and colors Available in 3 models and 43 color variants MD1 - M M1 Show details add to favorites chrome finish metal barrel, tip and push-button, solid colour clip with glossy finish MD1 - M M4 Show details add to favorites titanium grey finish metal barrel, tip and push-button, solid colour clip with glossy finish MD1 - M M2 Show details add to favorites gold finish metal barrel, tip and push-button, solid colour clip with glossy finish 3/4 Technical information Print areas and tech specs Features ● retractable with return spring ● metal push-button, barrel and tip, individually processed with diamond mirror face finish ● clip made of non-toxic, highly resistant ABS plastic ● “Parker type” refill, blue and black ink Modularity you can combine differently coloured parts from the same version (or code number), or elements from different versions A push-button B clip C barrel D tip Print areas 1 laser engraving 30 x 7 mm 2 pad printing 40 x 9 mm 4/4 Customisations The brands mentioned in this catalogue are the exclusive property of the respective owners. They are used for purely illustrative purposes and cannot be the object of any buying and selling transactions, under any circumstances. via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com MAXEMA SRL P.IVA 05321380015 privacy policy var acceptText='Accetto'; var policy_url='/cookie_privacy_policy/en'; var cookie_message='Il sito www.maxema.com utilizza cookie esclusivamente tecnici per permettere una corretta navigazione e la completa fruizione di tutti i contenuti da parte dell\\'utente. Non utilizziamo in alcun modo cookie di profilazione.'; var acceptText='I Understand'; var policy_url='/cookie_privacy_policy/en'; var cookie_message='This site uses cookies to improve their services and experience of readers. If you decide to continue browsing we consider that you accept their use.'; $(document).ready(function(){ $.cookieBar({ message: cookie_message, acceptButton: true, acceptText: acceptText, policyButton: true, policyText: 'Privacy Policy', policyURL: policy_url, autoEnable: true, acceptOnContinue: false, acceptOnScroll: false, acceptAnyClick: false, expireDays: 365, renewOnVisit: false, forceShow: false, bottom:true, fixed:true, domain: 'www.maxema.com', referrer: 'www.maxema.com' });